<paragraph blockId="12.[136,1059,1538,1657]" lastBlockId="13.[151,1074,1569,1656]" lastPageId="13" lastPageNumber="220" pageId="12" pageNumber="219">
<materialsCitation country="Thailand" county="Chinese" lastPageId="13" lastPageNumber="220" location="However" municipality="Therefore" pageId="12" pageNumber="219" specimenCount="1">
spermathecae with pilose apices and the ovoid receptacula separated from one other. 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:423C87CFE251FFC5FF517631FD2BEB60:CF4A6002E256FFC7FF4E7545FF59EC63" box="[136,235,1570,1593]" country="Thailand" county="Chinese" municipality="Therefore" name="However" pageId="12" pageNumber="219">However</location>
, the female examined slightly differ in the shape of the apices on the bulbose sacs which are round and clearly separate from the remaining membranous parts by thickenings (Figs 26, 29). 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:423C87CFE251FFC5FF517631FD2BEB60:CF4A6002E256FFC7FE657505FE7EEC23" box="[419,460,1634,1657]" country="Thailand" county="Chinese" municipality="Therefore" name="The" pageId="12" pageNumber="219">The</location>
separation is indistinct and the thickening of the apices is not prominent in females of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wang &amp; Yin" authorityYear="1985" box="[519,628,1569,1592]" class="Insecta" family="Tachinidae" genus="Hersilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="220" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="striata">
<emphasis box="[519,628,1569,1592]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="220">H. striata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<collectingMunicipality box="[647,755,1569,1592]" pageId="13" pageNumber="220">Therefore</collectingMunicipality>
, the female examined from 
<collectingCountry box="[151,246,1601,1624]" name="Thailand" pageId="13" pageNumber="220">Thailand</collectingCountry>
cannot be identified with certainty pending an examination of the 
<collectingCounty box="[988,1074,1601,1624]" pageId="13" pageNumber="220">Chinese</collectingCounty>
<typeStatus box="[151,211,1633,1656]" pageId="13" pageNumber="220">types</typeStatus>
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
